advantageous to get passed on,

63
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:48,655
including to cross, so that
multiple new traits can emerge

64
00:02:48,655 --> 00:02:51,330
from different parents in
these family trees.

65
00:02:51,330 --> 00:02:55,610
This facet of recombination is
such an advantage that some

66
00:02:55,610 --> 00:02:59,180
asexually reproducing, single
cell animals, will actually

67
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:02,409
