101
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:25,000
Looking Glass.

102
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,920
In the book, Alice and the Red
Queen are in a race, running

103
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,629
as fast as they can.

104
00:04:29,629 --> 00:04:32,719
And Alice at one point realises
that she doesn't seem

