113
00:04:53,329 --> 00:04:56,399
Evolution is a bit like this
race between Alice and the Red

114
00:04:56,399 --> 00:04:59,649
Queen, where species have to
run as fast as they can to

115
00:04:59,649 --> 00:05:01,049
stay in one place.

116
00:05:01,050 --> 00:05:04,939
Even a species that looks like
it's not changing, in fact may

117
00:05:04,939 --> 00:05:08,540
be undergoing constant variation
and change, or else

118
00:05:08,540 --> 00:05:13,300
the predators, the viruses, the
bacteria will catch up.

119
00:05:13,300 --> 00:05:16,270
A species like the horseshoe
crab, which is apparently

120
00:05:16,269 --> 00:05:19,609
