away from competitors.

144
00:06:19,670 --> 00:06:23,030
And it's so bright that it's
easy to pick out in the bush

145
00:06:23,029 --> 00:06:24,319
or in the forest.

146
00:06:24,319 --> 00:06:25,939
You can see it very clearly.

147
00:06:25,939 --> 00:06:28,939
Darwin at first couldn't
understand how an animal with

148
00:06:28,939 --> 00:06:32,129
this kind of trait could
possibly survive.

149
00:06:32,129 --> 00:06:34,202
If you've ever been around them
