166
00:07:13,199 --> 00:07:16,829
The females choose which
males they mate with.

167
00:07:16,829 --> 00:07:20,050
And so the preferences of the
females become accentuated in

168
00:07:20,050 --> 00:07:22,470
the males that successfully
reproduce.

169
00:07:22,470 --> 00:07:25,400
To successfully reproduce if
you're a male, you need a very

170
00:07:25,399 --> 00:07:28,329
