178
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,410
aren't as impressive.

179
00:07:46,410 --> 00:07:49,460
Now, it's not just tails that
animals use for this.

180
00:07:49,459 --> 00:07:52,629
In all kinds of species we find
